reviewText: this is deffinately one of my favourite dvd.great presentation by jenny jenny that makes the consert full of life...big up also to the other presenter...i,ve bought chezidek cd's after seeing his performance here.the sound quality is exelent and ...men!!!...It's areal musical vibe that will keep you entertained....highly recommended to all and a must have to all roots lovers!
Luciano, Richie Spice, Chezidek, etc. Great artists, production and great sound. Best quality of live Reggae performance on DVD. Recommend this DVD to any true Reggae Lover. JAH Bless
